Class ModelFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • Factories.ModelFactory

  • public class ModelFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for creating all instances of the model implementations that can be found in the model package using lazy instantiation It also has a get method for each model to return the instance of it
